{"tid":2406079,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【有傷心出殯南亞軍日日咪出動？】 店員提醒戴好口罩　南亞漢掃跌蛋糕險惹官非","createTime":"2021-02-13T02:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T08:40:08.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5e07139e58bed46fea5b8178b1272ed229350bc4","tid":2406079,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"今日(13日)大年初二凌晨1時許，一名戴口罩欠妥當的47歲南亞漢，進入旺角旺角道21號地下一間便利店購物。期間姓余(27歲)男店員見狀，提醒對方戴妥口罩時疑不精通英語，用廣東話跟對方溝通又「雞同鴨講」，南亞漢遂用身體語言回覆，惟揮手期間掃跌一個蛋糕致其飛出店外，店員誤以為南亞漢企圖店舖盜竊，即時報警求助。警方接報趕至，南亞漢已經戴好口罩，經初步調查後，相信事件屬誤會，在登記雙方資料後，南亞漢獲准離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/tgjsdztg.1et5e3pgfij.jbrke5dq5uh.xdc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Ftgjsdztg.1et5e3pgfij.jbrke5dq5uh.xdc.jpg&h=3fca77d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fd3de5cc6fce3c3e6df924a697e3f083fcd3059","tid":2406079,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"叫我&quot;do&quot;乜鳩電話？ 斬撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/18/cwE2HJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F18%2FcwE2HJ.png&h=b8898ba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed3e011d30c57924bf0627075e5fb2a9d9ee3844","tid":2406079,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"南亞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi